(27, 1393, 'en', 'description', '<p>Electrox is a progressive employer in the field of laser marking equipment manufacturing&nbsp;and is always interested in highly qualified individuals with experience in a wide range of disciplines including; laser design and development, software programming and sales and marketing. Send your career r&eacute;sum&eacute; to&nbsp;<a href="mailto:sales.uk@electrox.com?subject=website%20submit%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9" style="color: rgb(102,102,102); text-decoration: underline">sales@electroxlaser.com</a> if you believe you have the skills and expertise required for our fast moving, high technology environment.</p>\r\n'),
