(79, 1399, 'en', 'description', '<p>Electrox systems enable the controlled laser marking, etching and engraving on a wide range of materials&nbsp;including plastics, metals, glass, wood and rubber.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Primary Applications for our lasers...</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="/applications/ablation">Ablation</a> and coating removal</li>\r\n	<li>Decorative design and personalisation</li>\r\n	<li>Traceability and identification</li>\r\n	<li>Authentication and labeling</li>\r\n	<li>Micro-machining</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n'),
