(89, 1400, 'en', 'description', '<p><strong>The 600 Group PLC (&quot;the Group&quot;) is a diversified engineering group with three principal areas of activity:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 749px;" width="100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width: 675px;">\r\n			<p><strong style="line-height: 1.6em;">Machine Tools</strong></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">The business has a strong reputation in the market for metal turning machines. Products range from small conventional machines for education markets, CNC workshop machines and CNC production machines. The manufacturing footprint is supported by selected outsourcing partners and machines are marketed through the Group&#39;s wholly owned international sales organisation.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width: 74px;">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">To view our main Machine Tool brands, please click on the links below:</span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><a href="http://www.colchester-harrison.com"><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">www.colchester-harrison.com</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><a href="http://www.clausing-industrial.com">www.clausing-industrial.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<p><strong>Precision Engineered Components</strong></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">Machine spares are distributed to customers globally to help maintain the installed base of group machines which number in excess of 100,000. Additionally, work holding products and taper roller bearings are sold via specialist distributors to OEMs, including other machine builders.</span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>To view our main Precision Engineered Component brands, please click on the links below:</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<p><a href="http://www.pratt-burnerd.co.uk">www.pratt-burnerd.co.uk</a></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><a href="http://www.gamet-bearings.com">www.gamet-bearings.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><a href="http://www.colchester-harrison.com">www.colchester-harrison.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n			<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 675px;" width="100%">\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td style="height: 53px;">\r\n						<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n						<p><strong>Laser Marking, Etching And Engraving</strong></p>\r\n\r\n						<p><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">Laser marking, etching and engraving are&nbsp;technologically superior alternatives to ink jet marking. They require&nbsp;no consumables and can operate on a continuous high speed basis when integrated into customers&#39; production lines. The business has its own technology and proprietary software. Customer applications are diverse and range from telecommunications to pharmaceuticals. The requirement for increased product and component traceability is one of the market drivers.</span></p>\r\n						</td>\r\n						<td style="height: 53px;">&nbsp;</td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<p><strong style="line-height: 1.6em;">Machine Tool Sales Locations</strong></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">600 Europe manufactures and distributes 600 Group machine tool products and precision engineered components with an international reputation for performance and quality.</span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><a href="http://www.600uk.com"><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">www.600uk.com</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">600 North America distributes Clausing and Colchester-Harrison machine tool products throughout the region, in addition to precision engineered components and laser spares.</span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><a href="http://www.clausing-industrial.com"><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">www.clausing-industrial.com</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">Pratt Burnerd America sells Pratt Burnerd workholding products throughout North America</span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><a href="http://www.pratt-burnerd.com"><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">www.pratt-burnerd.com</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">600 Machinery International covers the middle east and north African regions</span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><a href="http://www.600mac.co.uk"><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">www.600mac.co.uk</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n			<p>600 Machine Tools PTY operates throughout Australia, New Zealand and the Pacific Rim regions</p>\r\n\r\n			<p><a href="http://www.600machinery.com.au/" style="line-height: 1.6em;">www.600machinery.com.au</a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n'),
