(99, 1401, 'en', 'description', '<p><strong>Electrox has&nbsp;developed strong and established international&nbsp;links with many&nbsp;trade and industry bodies.&nbsp; Please click on the selected&nbsp;links below to find out more about the Laser Marking, Etching and Engraving&nbsp;industry.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>Microglyph</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Developers of the microglyph&reg; 2D code which adapts to the geometry of a surface making it particularly suitable for industrial direct-part-marking applications</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://www.microglyphs.com/">www.microglyphs.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Engineering Employers Federation EEF</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The manufacturers&#39; organisation representing the interests of manufacturing, engineering and technology-based businesses</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://www.eef.co.uk/">www.eef.co.uk</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Laser Institute of America</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The professional membership society dedicated to fostering interest in lasers, laser applications and laser safety worldwide</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://www.laserinstitute.org/">www.laserinstitute.org</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Manufacturing Technologies Association</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The national organisation representing companies in the UK machine tool and manufacturing technology sector</p>\r\n'),
