(591, 1448, 'en', 'process_description', 'The specific data marked on a pacemaker has to be clearly legible throughout the lifetime of the device, which can be many years. That data typically includes critical information such as the manufacturer, model and serial number of the unit being marked. A manufacturer''s logo or brand mark is also often marked using this method. '),
